hift_codes_q1 data-internalLink=true>What are SHiFT Codes?</a><li><a href=#faq_shift_codes_q2 data-internalLink=true>Where are SHiFT Codes released?</a><li><a href=#faq_shift_codes_q3 data-internalLink=true>How often are SHiFT Codes released?</a><li><a href=#faq_shift_codes_q4 data-internalLink=true>Do SHiFT Codes ever expire?</a><li><a href=#faq_shift_codes_q5 data-internalLink=true>How many times can a SHiFT Code be redeemed?</a><li><a href=#faq_shift_codes_q6 data-internalLink=true>What games support SHiFT Codes?</a></ul></div><div class=section><a href=#faq_shiftcodestk data-internalLink=true class=title>ShiftCodesTK</a><ul><li><a href=#faq_shiftcodestk_q1 data-internalLink=true>Is ShiftCodesTK affiliated with Gearbox or 2K?</a><li><a href=#faq_shiftcodestk_q2 data-internalLink=true>Can you create a SHiFT Code for me? Can you change the properties of a SHiFT Code? Can you give me a legendary?</a><li><a href=#faq_shiftcodestk_q3 data-internalLink=true>Do you have any information on future titles, expansions, or events related to Borderlands?</a></ul></div></header><section id=faq_shift><header><h2>SHiFT</h2></header><div class=qa id=faq_shift_q1><h3>What is SHiFT?</h3><p>SHiFT is a service created by Gearbox to reward their players with in-game loot and special events.</div><div class=qa id=faq_shift_q2><h3>Do you need an account to use SHiFT?</h3><p>Yes. You can create a free accountÂ <a href=https://shift.gearboxsoftware.com/registration/pre aria-label="Register for SHiFT"rel="external noopener"target=_blank title="Register for SHiFT"><span class="fa-external-link-square-alt fas"aria-label="External Link"title="External Link"></span><span class=label>here</span></a>.</div><div class=qa id=faq_shift_q3><h3>How old do you need to be to use SHiFT?</h3><p>You must be at least 18 years old to sign up for SHiFT.</div></section><section id=faq_shift_codes><header><h2>SHiFT Codes</h2></header><div class=qa id=faq_shift_codes_q1><h3>What are SHiFT Codes</h3><p>SHiFT Codes are 25-character keys that grant in-game rewards.</div><div class=qa id=faq_shift_codes_q2><h3>Where are SHiFT Codes released?</h3><p>SHiFT Codes are typically released on Twitter and Facebook via official handles, but are also sometimes released during special events and livestreams.</div><div class=qa id=faq_shift_codes_q3><h3>How often are SHiFT Codes released?</h3><p>SHiFT Codes are typically released every Friday around 10AM PST.</div><div class=qa id=faq_shift_codes_q4><h3>Do SHiFT Codes ever expire?</h3><p>Yes, most SHiFT Codes will be issued with an Expiration Date, typically about two to three weeks after their release. However, some SHiFT Codes have and can be issued without an Expiration Date.</div><div class=qa id=faq_shift_codes_q5><h3>How many times can a SHiFT Code be redeemed?</h3><p>SHiFT Codes can be redeemed once per account.</div><div class=qa id=faq_shift_codes_q6><h3>What games support SHiFT Codes?</h3><p>The following titles support SHiFT Codes:<ul><li>Borderlands 2<li>Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel<li>Borderlands: Game of the Year Edition</ul><p><em>There are other titles that accept SHiFT Codes, such as Battleborn, but they are not supported on ShiftCodesTK.</em></div></section><section id=faq_shiftcodestk><header><h2>ShiftCodesTK</h2></header><div class=qa id=faq_shiftcodestk_q1><h3>Is ShiftCodesTK affiliated with Gearbox or 2K?</h3><p>Nope, ShiftCodesTK is a completely fan-made service, and is not affiliated with Gearbox Software or 2K Games in any way.</div><div class=qa id=faq_shiftcodestk_q2><h3>Can you create a SHiFT Code for me? Can you change the properties of a SHiFT Code? Can you give me a legendary?</h3><p>No, we have no control over the SHiFT Codes themselves, and just share the codes released by Gearbox.</div><div class=qa id=faq_shiftcodestk_q3><h3>Do you have any information on future titles, expansions, or events related to Borderlands?</h3><p>Nope, we have no information on anything regarding the future of Borderlands.</div></section></main><div class=help-footer><h2 class=header>Still have questions?</h2><div class=body><div class="panel contact"><h3 class=title>Contact us</h3><div class=button-wrapper><a href=https://m.me/ShiftCodesTK aria-label="Contact us on Facebook (External Link)"rel="external noopener"target=_blank title="Contact us on Facebook (External Link)"><span class="icon fab fa-facebook-messenger"></span><span class=label><span>Contact us</span><span>on Facebook</span></span></a><a href="https://twitter.com/messages/compose?recipient_id=3830990053"aria-label="Contact us on Twitter (External Link)"rel="external noopener"target=_blank title="Contact us on Twitter (External Link)"><span class="icon fab fa-twitter"></span><span class=label><span>Contact us</span><span>on Twitter</span></span></a></div></div><div class="panel external"><h3 class=title>Get additional support</h3><div class=button-wrapper><a href=http://support.gearboxsoftware.com aria-label="Visit the official Gearbox Support website (External Link)"rel="external noopener"target=_blank title="Visit the official Gearbox Support website (External Link)"><span class="icon fa-external-link-square-alt fas"></span><span class=label><span>Visit Gearbox</span><span>Support site</span></span></a><a href=https://support.2k.com aria-label="Visit the official 2K Games Support website (External Link)"rel="external noopener"target=_blank title="Visit the official 2K Games Support website (External Link)"><span class="icon fa-external-link-square-alt fas"></span><span class=label><span>Visit 2K</span><span>Support site</span></span></a></div></div></div></div><?php include_once('./assets/php/html/min/imports/global/afterContent.php'); ?>